preAlphaText:
Welcomz to Cosmic Reach! 
 Da gaem iz in very early development, itz missin' features, iz nowhere near complete, 
 nd will likely haz bugs, glitches, crashes nd wurld corruption.
 Everything iz subject to change nd iz not representative of da final gaem.
 Itz available for ya to play so dat ya can gib feedback to halp guide da future of dis game 
 Happy testin'... nd game-breakin'!
No_Clip: b able to walkz thru wallz
Fullscreen: turn on nd off teh fullzcrin
Return_to_Main_Menu: go bak to da main menu
MAC_warning: WARNING: Mac iz not supported at dis time. Teh gaem iz unlikely to werk.

detected!

nd will be improved in latur updates.
Loading: Cat god iz preparin ur wurld
Tip15: Tip: Pick block usin' teh middle mouse button!
Tip16: Tip: Try changin' teh different lightin' modes in teh pause menu!
Tip17: Tip: Press '$keybind_hideUI' to hide teh user interface
Tip18: Tip: Press '$keybind_screenshot' to mak funny picz!
Tip19: Tip: Press '$keybind_debugInfo' to look at teh debuggin' information
Tip20: Tip: Press '$keybind_dropItem' to drop teh current item!
Tip21: Tip: Press '$keybind_openInventory' to open teh secret fur pouch!
Tip22: Tip: Sprint against a wall to 'wall run', goin' farther than you would only by jumpin'.
OddTip11: Tip: U cannot fight against teh entropy.
